  ('medical-tech-moex-00127', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-112-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '若一超音波頻率為5 MHz，且每個脈衝（pulse）包含2個週波數（cycle），則此超音波在軟組織傳導之脈衝長 度（spatial pulse length, SPL）為多少毫米（mm）？', '["0.308", "0.616", "0.924", "1.541"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58240add829d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6ef8a5ef1005", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112020", "c": "308", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00128', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-112-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關臨床生理檢查的敘述，下列何者最不適當？', '["2個月內有發生過心肌梗塞之病患可以用運動心電圖檢查", "猝睡症（narcolepsy）的患者在進行多次入睡檢查（multiple sleep latency test）時，常會出現過早發生之快速動 眼期", "失神小發作（petit mal）常以腦波檢查的快速深呼吸法誘發出來", "重複神經刺激檢查常用於評估神經肌肉接合處的病變"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58240add829d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6ef8a5ef1005", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112020", "c": "308", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
